<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Reset Your Password</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px;">
<div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
  <h2 style="color: #333;">Reset your password</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555;">
    We received a request to reset your password. If you made this request, please click the button below:
  </p>
  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{resetLink}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #007bff; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">
      Reset Password
    </a>
  </div>
  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #777;">
    If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.
  </p>
  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #777;">This link will expire after a short time for security reasons.</p>
  <p style="color: #999999; font-size: 14px;">
    If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:
  </p>
  <p style="color: #007BFF; word-break: break-all;">
    {{resetLink}}
  </p>
  <hr />
</div>
</body>
</html>
